不要做個只懂伸手的廢物)，而光速已經大得可以把相機希望獲取的資訊甩在你車尾燈也看不到的位置，所以，只要你下次記得把車子開到光速，你就不用怕被人拍快相了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7798a287f95b17447e81fc0df4e7878364bf0ad","tid":2457221,"uid":229954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f0a55f65abfbdfa64883cb76fe8e0c4e4bcb2","tid":2457221,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81358b66d334d60eb61c66152b16612d7c3fbcd8","tid":2457221,"uid":80183,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"昂船州大橋周不時有160-170電單車飛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔怕死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"昂船州有冇相機？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"隧道唔知<br />\n但係橋去到西隧口都無"},{"pid":"0ec6c845dac58b78694414e8a73d5961be06b1f7","tid":2457221,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7798a287f95b17447e81fc0df4e7878364bf0ad","tid":2457221,"uid":229954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f0a55f65abfbdfa64883cb76fe8e0c4e4bcb2","tid":2457221,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81358b66d334d60eb61c66152b16612d7c3fbcd8","tid":2457221,"uid":80183,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"昂船州大橋周不時有160-170電單車飛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔怕死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"昂船州有冇相機？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"隧道唔知<br />\n但係橋去到西隧口都無"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"汀九出九龍有連續三個<br />\n南灣去到西隧無<br />\n<br />\n汀九往元朗橋頭有一個<br />\n<br />\n其他無"},{"pid":"1f66fd8c3e6fa5bfed7019974d0c279a5969b761","tid":2457221,"uid":114994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c0f6aee8be5925cbac36b0414130f18ff72685d","tid":2457221,"uid":294,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3529450a5bc4e0da589e9c13b5cd1839c16815ea","tid":2457221,"uid":85097,"like"